title: Young man and his Aunt & Uncle observe large tracks just below their horse pasture in Tehachapi (w/photos)
observed: As my Uncle walked outside to feed the horse he spotted tracks. They were big huge prints! The measurements are 52" inch strides, with indication of toe's at the end, and hair like lines throughout the bottom. I do have the address, because the prints are on my property.
location_details: Bear Valley Springs, CA, located in Tehachapi, Ca.
